      "name": "Bethany Atazadeh",
      "content": "<p><strong>Platform + URL:</strong> YouTube &mdash; search https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=bethany+atazadeh</p><p><strong>Approx reach:</strong> Not verified</p><p><strong>Covers:</strong> YA author coaching writers on writing, editing, self-publishing, and marketing; \"Author Money\" and \"Outline With Me\" series.</p><p><strong>IdiamPro angle:</strong> Her live \"Outline With Me\" format maps 1:1 onto IdiamPro's outline-first book pipeline.</p><p><strong>&#9888; Confirm before outreach:</strong> Verify her exact channel handle before reaching out &mdash; canonical channel URL not yet landed.</p>",
