      "name": "Curious Refuge — AI Screenwriting (Screenwriting)",
      "content": "<p><strong>Platform + URL:</strong> https://curiousrefuge.com/ai-screenwriting</p><p><strong>Covers:</strong> Course + community teaching concept &rarr; pitch deck &rarr; finished script. The clearest real home for AI-screenwriting education (cross-listed with AI Video & Filmmaking).</p><p><strong>IdiamPro angle:</strong> IdiamPro's screenplay output + outline spine is a direct fit.</p><p><strong>&#9888; Candid note:</strong> Beyond Curious Refuge, screenwriting-with-AI is dominated by <em>tools</em>, not individual creator-voices. No strong standalone screenwriter-creator verified &mdash; a gap worth manual hunting on YouTube.</p>",
