      "content": "<p><strong>Platform + URL:</strong> https://www.legaltechdigest.org</p><p><strong>Covers:</strong> Weekly legal-tech newsletter for lawyers/students; features tools practitioners can adopt.</p><p><strong>IdiamPro angle:</strong> A natural place for an IdiamPro legal-doc demo.</p>",
