      "name": "Matt Wolfe (cross-listed)",
      "content": "<p><strong>Platform + URL:</strong> https://www.youtube.com/@mreflow</p><p><strong>Covers:</strong> Also heavily covers AI image tools (see AI Explainers & Education for full entry).</p><p><strong>IdiamPro angle:</strong> Natural home for an \"outline &rarr; AI mind-map / diagram / graphics\" demo.</p>",
